Package com.millicast

Interface Subscriber.Listener

All Superinterfaces:
Client.Listener
Enclosing class:
Subscriber
public static interface Subscriber.Listener extends Client.Listener
The Listener struct for the Subscriber class. It adds the onSubscribed event on top of the Client listener You must inherit this class and set a listener with setListener to be able to receive events from the Subscriber.
